24:51.791 --> 24:53.858
You better change
your clothes.

24:53.860 --> 24:55.926
No john will open his purse
if he can't see the goods.

24:55.928 --> 24:58.562
No, um, we're not...

24:58.564 --> 25:00.898
What term is
your preference?
Term?

25:00.900 --> 25:02.733
For your profession.

25:02.735 --> 25:05.035
Harlot. Whore.

25:05.037 --> 25:07.204
Courtesan has a nice ring
to it, fancy-like.

25:07.206 --> 25:09.206
Well, then we are
not courtesans.

25:09.208 --> 25:11.208
We're actually here to see
your mistress, greer.

25:11.210 --> 25:12.843
I'll fetch her.

25:12.845 --> 25:15.579
