leave it here, and go.

25:25.858 --> 25:26.857
He's here.

25:26.859 --> 25:27.858
Who?

25:27.860 --> 25:29.827
That general
I met, renaude.

25:29.829 --> 25:32.830
You go ahead, and I'll
give greer the fabric.

25:32.832 --> 25:35.599
And leave you eyeing
a man in a whorehouse?

25:35.601 --> 25:37.234
Does that sound
like a good idea?

25:37.236 --> 25:38.869
I'm not gonna do anything.

25:38.871 --> 25:40.838
Go ahead, I-I'll just be
with you in a moment.

25:40.840 --> 25:44.909
â™ª I can't take this place

25:44.911 --> 25:47.044
â™ª no, I can't take this place

25:47.046 --> 25:49.046
â™ª I just want to go

25:49.048 --> 25:51.949
â™ª where I can get
some space... â™ª

25:54.219 --> 25:56.220
Lady lola.

