but I assumed I was mistaken.

25:59.859 --> 26:02.259
What reason could
a court lady have

26:02.261 --> 26:04.795
For visiting a
known whorehouse?

26:04.797 --> 26:08.165
The mind vibrates with
the possibilities.

26:08.167 --> 26:11.001
I don't have to explain
my comings and goings to you,

26:11.003 --> 26:12.903
But if you must know,

26:12.905 --> 26:14.271
I was delivering
some cloth to a friend.

26:14.273 --> 26:16.607
Your fallen friend,
lady greer.

26:16.609 --> 26:18.842
I hear that she
is the proprietor

26:18.844 --> 26:21.312
Of this establishment--
industrious girl.

26:21.314 --> 26:24.081
Women often have to be,
in order to survive.

26:24.083 --> 26:25.916
They also need
to be careful.

26:25.918 --> 26:27.985
Even making
friendly deliveries.

26:27.987 --> 26:31.822
Tongues less discreet
than my own will wag.

26:31.824 --> 26:34.358
Even for the mother of
the king's only child.

26:34.360 --> 26:37.828
You mean especially for a woman
known as the king's mistress.

26:37.830 --> 26:41.031
Word of your loyalty
to mary has spread.

26:41.033 --> 26:42.866
You have risen above

26:42.868 --> 26:44.868
Any negative speculation
there was about you.

26:44.870 --> 26:47.104
Your son is esteemed.

26:47.106 --> 26:50.307
Do not let anything
diminish this position

26:50.309 --> 26:52.142
That you have earned.

26:52.144 --> 26:54.845
Why do you care?

26:54.847 --> 26:57.281
I don't know.

26:59.684 --> 27:01.385
But I do.

27:05.824 --> 27:10.661
I would escort you back if
I were still welcome at court,

27:10.663 --> 27:12.029
But, sadly, I'm not.

27:13.098 --> 27:14.298
Good night, lola.

27:26.645 --> 27:28.278
Greer: Thank you
for the beautiful fabric.

27:28.280 --> 27:29.980
Kenna:
Of course.

27:29.982 --> 27:31.849
Did that man
just put on...
A collar, yes.

27:31.851 --> 27:33.250
He likes to be led around.

27:33.252 --> 27:36.920
Death and perversion are
the two great equalizers.

27:36.922 --> 27:38.122
Men from all walks
of life have

27:38.124 --> 27:40.090
Their own desires
and predilections.

27:40.092 --> 27:43.293
And as long as they don't cause
harm, I cater to all of them.

27:45.664 --> 27:46.830
And, uh, what about him?

27:46.832 --> 27:47.898
What's his pleasure?

27:49.000 --> 27:50.434
General renaude?

27:50.436 --> 27:52.936
It's the first time
he's come in.

27:52.938 --> 27:54.938
He and his men overtook
the rebels at the monastery.

27:54.940 --> 27:56.173
Now he's treating them
to the best champagne

27:56.175 --> 27:57.908
And women money can buy.

27:57.910 --> 27:59.810
Generous.

27:59.812 --> 28:01.712
It's the least
he could do.

28:01.714 --> 28:05.015
My girls overheard
his men grumbling.

28:05.017 --> 28:08.185
His right-hand man was killed,
some say unnecessarily.

28:08.187 --> 28:10.187
They blame him.
Why?

28:10.189 --> 28:12.089
There were two groups
of boys that needed saving.

28:12.091 --> 28:13.991
He chose the riskier path
to save the son

28:13.993 --> 28:16.160
Of a very rich noble.

28:16.162 --> 28:18.429
His man died as a result.

28:18.431 --> 28:21.765
If I were you, I'd keep
my distance from him.

28:33.078 --> 28:34.211
You seem troubled.

28:34.213 --> 28:36.814
Not at all.

28:36.816 --> 28:39.049
I'm only surprised at how fast
things are progressing.

28:39.051 --> 28:40.884
There'll be time
for a celebration later.

28:40.886 --> 28:44.254
As I said, queen elizabeth
desires an expeditious union.

28:46.224 --> 28:47.925
Look alive.

28:47.927 --> 28:50.327
It's not every day a man
gets to marry a queen.

28:59.804 --> 29:03.874
