from my boots â™ª

29:07.112 --> 29:11.181
â™ª try not to feel the cold

29:14.886 --> 29:17.988
â™ª caught in the thought

29:17.990 --> 29:21.458
â™ª of that time

29:21.460 --> 29:23.460
â™ª that everything was fine

29:23.462 --> 29:25.295
â™ª everything was mine...

29:25.297 --> 29:27.998
Take this to lord condÃ©'s
apartments in the village.

29:28.000 --> 29:32.069
Do not make any stops
on your way.

29:33.238 --> 29:35.305
And deliver it directly
to his hands.

29:37.776 --> 29:40.077
â™ª all the king's horses
and all the king's men... â™ª

