As represented
by her appointed proxy.

29:49.955 --> 29:52.322
Despite the great distance

29:52.324 --> 29:53.924
Between the groom
and the bride,

29:53.926 --> 29:56.927
These rites and vows
will be as binding

29:56.929 --> 29:59.396
As if you were standing
